======================================

Instructions for Compiling and Running
--------------------------------------
untar code and libraries
make to compile code 
./RTRT to run

Keyboard Controls
--------------------------------------
wasd  - movement

q     - reset camera
r     - redraw spheres
o     - spiral inwards
p     - spiral outwards
[     - orbit camera CW
]     - orbit camera CCW
+     - increase sphere size
=     - decrease sphere size
9     - darkens planes
0     - brightens planes

Mouse Controls
--------------------------------------
Click mouse and drag   - turning


To make changes in sphere numbers, edit cudaRayTrace.h
